{"id":"api/platform-browser/animations/async/provideAnimationsAsync","title":"provideAnimationsAsync","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/platform-browser\", \"name\": \"@angular/platform-browser\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/platform-browser/animations/async\", \"name\": \"@angular/platform-browser/animations/async\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 4, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/platform-browser/animations/async/provideAnimationsAsync\", \"name\": \"provideAnimationsAsync\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/platform-browser\">@angular/platform-browser</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/async\">@angular/platform-browser/animations/async</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/platform-browser/animations/async/src/providers.ts#L14-L59\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"provideanimationsasync\">provideAnimationsAsync<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/async/provideAnimationsAsync#provideanimationsasync\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    <label class=\"api-status-label dev-preview\" title=\"此 API 僅供開發者預覽\">\n      <a href=\"guide/releases#developer-preview\">開發者預覽</a>\n    </label>\n    \n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"b7j3m95q8ffz2g1j4c5wey69z\">回傳一組<a href=\"guide/glossary#provider\">依賴注入提供程式</a>以在應用程式中啟用動畫。請參閱<a href=\"guide/animations\">動畫指南</a>以瞭解有關 Angular 中動畫的更多訊息。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/async/provideAnimationsAsync#description\">檢視更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/async/provideAnimationsAsync\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideAnimationsAsync</a></span>(type: \"animations\" | \"noop\" = 'animations'): <a href=\"api/core/EnvironmentProviders\" class=\"code-anchor\">EnvironmentProviders</a></code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7zgytlpr676in397zep1nxg0l\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>type</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>\"animations\" | \"noop\"</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9n9al9z9kpkphbp8es3txryg3\">傳遞 \n<code>'noop'</code> 作為引數來停用動畫。</p>\n\n        <p>可選值。預設值為 <code>'animations'</code>。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">回傳值</h6>\n  <p><code><a href=\"api/core/EnvironmentProviders\" class=\"code-anchor\">EnvironmentProviders</a></code></p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/async/provideAnimationsAsync#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9wqnbu68irgiaseyh4pmfsoe3\">當你使用該函式而不是急性 \n<code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/provideAnimations\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideAnimations</a>()</code> 時，動畫不會在渲染器載入前渲染。</p>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a1taehcj5epmrpo4w613v5en9\">更多訊息請參閱 \n<a href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/async/provideAnimationsAsync#usage-notes\">使用說明...</a></p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/async/provideAnimationsAsync#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4o1fjz7h58gf1whq8v0ukaxtj\">當你想要在使用 <code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a></code> 函式引導的應用程式中啟用動畫時，該函式很有用。在這種情況下，根本不需要匯入 <code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/BrowserAnimationsModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">BrowserAnimationsModule</a></code> NgModule，只需將此函式回傳的提供者新增到 <code>providers</code> 清單中，如下所示。</p>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\n<a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a>(RootComponent, {\n  providers: [\n    <a href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/async/provideAnimationsAsync\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideAnimationsAsync</a>()\n  ]\n});\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/platform-browser/animations/async\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/EnvironmentProviders\n - api/platform-browser\n - api/platform-browser/animations/BrowserAnimationsModule\n - api/platform-browser/animations/async\n - api/platform-browser/animations/async/provideAnimationsAsync#description\n - api/platform-browser/animations/async/provideAnimationsAsync#provideanimationsasync\n - api/platform-browser/animations/async/provideAnimationsAsync#usage-notes\n - api/platform-browser/animations/provideAnimations\n - api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\n - guide/animations\n - guide/glossary#provider\n - guide/releases#developer-preview\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/platform-browser/animations/async/src/providers.ts#L14-L59\n-->"}